### ============================================================
### EVENTS — Important Events (Customers only)
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### All endpoints require a customer JWT access token
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = PASTE_CUSTOMER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@otherUserToken = PASTE_OTHER_USER_TOKEN_HERE
@courierToken = PASTE_COURIER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# CREATE IMPORTANT EVENT
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Create Event — one-time birthday event
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sara's Birthday",
  "event_date": "2026-09-20",
  "recurring": false
}

###

### [SUCCESS] Create Event — recurring anniversary
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Wedding Anniversary",
  "event_date": "2026-06-05",
  "recurring": true
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Create Event — no token (401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Secret Event",
  "event_date": "2026-07-01",
  "recurring": false
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Create Event — missing required title (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_date": "2026-07-01",
  "recurring": false
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Create Event — invalid date format (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bad Date Event",
  "event_date": "not-a-date",
  "recurring": false
}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# LIST MY EVENTS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] List Events — authenticated customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [SUCCESS] List Events — with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/?skip=0&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] List Events — no token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/

###

### [FAIL — Validation] List Events — limit exceeds max (422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/?limit=9999
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET SPECIFIC EVENT
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get Event — owner retrieves their event
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Event — IDOR: another user tries to get this event (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Get Event — non-existent event ID (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# UPDATE EVENT
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Update Event — change title and date
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sara's Birthday (updated)",
  "event_date": "2026-09-21",
  "recurring": true
}

###

### [SUCCESS] Update Event — partial update (only title)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mom's Birthday"
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Update Event — another user updates someone else's event (404)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hijacked Event"
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Update Event — no token (401)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Unauthorized Update"
}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# DELETE EVENT
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Delete Event — owner deletes their own event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Delete Event — IDOR: another user deletes someone else's event (404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Delete Event — non-existent event (404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Delete Event — no token (401)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/1
